        <abstract> 
<p>Their enumeration [of forms of <hi rend="italic">Lythrum</hi>?] is invaluable. He will write later to explain what he is trying to prove about <hi rend="italic">Lythrum</hi> through laborious crosses.</p>  
<p>Asks for flowers of both forms of <hi rend="italic">Hottonia</hi> to measure pollen and compare stigmas.</p> 
